item.title: ~~How do I change the death spawn point!?!?~~
item.dc:creator: @X-J-K-X X-J-K-X
item.description:
@X-J-K-X wrote:

Ok first off. On your server. Die. Get someone to kill you. Then, on moparscape client. Or if you have a command to show your coords. Like ::mypos. Or what ever. Do that, as soon as you die, where you spawn. If using mopar client, use ::coordson.

Okay now, get the X coord…

Next, go to client.java. Ctrl + F. And type…

teleportToX = XCOORD;

It should be something close to that. Or teleX = XCOORD;

What ever it might be. Okay now, before changing anything. Keep searching, just incase you find that X coord to be something else in your server.

After checking all the X coords. Look for one that will be most appropriate in this situation. Prefrebly applyDead, or in a method.

Kay, you should see something like

teleportToX = ####;
teleportToY = ####;

Finally, change those coords to the new coords ( New place when you die )…

And your done.

Hav a nise day.
